<% @title = "Technical Information about Viewr" %>
<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Architecture</h2>
</div>
<p>Viewr runs on a FreeBSD jail kindly provided by <a href="http://www.multiplay.co.uk">Multiplay</a>.</p>
<p>Viewr consists of:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Rails 3.1.1 application (ruby 1.9.3) serving these pages</li>
  <li>MySQL database server</li>
  <li>Ruby daemon using daemon-kit polling various sources</li>
  <li>Faye client and server using pub/sub for messaging</li>
</ul>
