<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Polling Intervals</h2>
</div>
<p>The below are the current polling settings for the backend of this
application. Any application/feed owners can ask these to be changed if
desperately required.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Twitter: 360 seconds (6 minutes)</li>
  <li>Forums RSS: 600 seconds (10 minutes)</li>
  <li>iseries Site news: 300 seconds (5 minutes)</li>
</ul>

